{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/32/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>WEB フォントの使い方について説明します。画像が多めの説明です。</p>\n<h2 id=\"サーバーに直接フォントをアップロード\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%82%B5%E3%83%BC%E3%83%90%E3%83%BC%E3%81%AB%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E3%83%95%E3%82%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88%E3%82%92%E3%82%A2%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89\" aria-label=\"サーバーに直接フォントをアップロード permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>サーバーに直接フォントをアップロード</h2>\n<h3 id=\"フォントを準備する\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%83%95%E3%82%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88%E3%82%92%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\" aria-label=\"フォントを準備する permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>フォントを準備する</h3>\n<p>まず使いたいフォントをローカルで用意します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/362af81592af8428fcdf9b19389cf7dd/9cab2/image.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/362af81592af8428fcdf9b19389cf7dd/0a47e/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/362af81592af8428fcdf9b19389cf7dd/8a4e8/image.png 150w,\n/static/362af81592af8428fcdf9b19389cf7dd/5a46d/image.png 300w,\n/static/362af81592af8428fcdf9b19389cf7dd/0a47e/image.png 600w,\n/static/362af81592af8428fcdf9b19389cf7dd/9cab2/image.png 864w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>必要ならばコンバーターを使用して変換もします。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://convertio.co/ja/font-converter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://convertio.co/ja/font-converter/</a></p>\n<p>準備ができたら<a href=\"https://forest.watch.impress.co.jp/library/software/ffftp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">FFFTP</a>等でサーバーにアップロードします。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/8a69d/image-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAXklEQVR42m2MSwrAIAxEe/9LVnARQwUjRFAUp4y7Qh+EJMznijFCJMG9YYyB3vvZIoInZ5RScIcAVT33Wusze29YNSRVzDlxmRlqrUckNJDWHO5+yllEH/8/6KHO7AuhW5rUjzRFSgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/0a47e/image-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/8a4e8/image-1.png 150w,\n/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/5a46d/image-1.png 300w,\n/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/0a47e/image-1.png 600w,\n/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/1cfc2/image-1.png 900w,\n/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/c1b63/image-1.png 1200w,\n/static/4d63e258e17ded311b1385874158520f/8a69d/image-1.png 1209w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"css-の記述\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-%E3%81%AE%E8%A8%98%E8%BF%B0\" aria-label=\"css の記述 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS の記述</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@font-face</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'HelveticaNeue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'font/HelveticaNeue-Thin.eot'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* IE9 Compat Modes */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">src</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'font/HelveticaNeue-Thin.eot?#iefix'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'embedded-opentype'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* IE6-IE8 */</span>\n      <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'font/HelveticaNeue-Thin.woff'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'woff'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/* Modern Browsers */</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'font/HelveticaNeue-Thin.ttf'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'truetype'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Safari, Android, iOS */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.txt</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'HelveticaNeue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>あらかじめ宣言しておいて、適用させたい部分で font-family で設定した名称を設定します。</p>\n<h2 id=\"adobe-fonts有料\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adobe-fonts%E6%9C%89%E6%96%99\" aria-label=\"adobe fonts有料 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adobe Fonts（有料）</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.adobe.com/my_fonts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://fonts.adobe.com/my_fonts</a></p>\n<p>Adobe CC に加入していると Adobe Fonts を無料で利用できます。\n今回は私の普段の使い方を例に説明します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/188782cade172f0b0461ca5c4168fb3e/2cffa/image-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/188782cade172f0b0461ca5c4168fb3e/0a47e/image-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/188782cade172f0b0461ca5c4168fb3e/8a4e8/image-2.png 150w,\n/static/188782cade172f0b0461ca5c4168fb3e/5a46d/image-2.png 300w,\n/static/188782cade172f0b0461ca5c4168fb3e/0a47e/image-2.png 600w,\n/static/188782cade172f0b0461ca5c4168fb3e/1cfc2/image-2.png 900w,\n/static/188782cade172f0b0461ca5c4168fb3e/2cffa/image-2.png 1092w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>使用したいフォントを選びます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/edb95b2457fc9b8f1bd06834de9ca4c6/cdec4/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/edb95b2457fc9b8f1bd06834de9ca4c6/b4294/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/edb95b2457