n: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 581px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5a702512f02da1bbc0a7325f4c470d50/92d15/image-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 99.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/5a702512f02da1bbc0a7325f4c470d50/92d15/image-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5a702512f02da1bbc0a7325f4c470d50/8a4e8/image-4.png 150w,\n/static/5a702512f02da1bbc0a7325f4c470d50/5a46d/image-4.png 300w,\n/static/5a702512f02da1bbc0a7325f4c470d50/92d15/image-4.png 581w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 581px) 100vw, 581px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>種類が多い場合は「＋さらに５個を表示」をクリックします。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 580px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7193a32c1794104b33222409c0ee30af/b6272/image-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 108.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/7193a32c1794104b33222409c0ee30af/b6272/image-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7193a32c1794104b33222409c0ee30af/8a4e8/image-5.png 150w,\n/static/7193a32c1794104b33222409c0ee30af/5a46d/image-5.png 300w,\n/static/7193a32c1794104b33222409c0ee30af/b6272/image-5.png 580w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>使用するフォントを選んだら作成します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 586px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3674485201d53f493a2977900a70367b/f8a08/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 134%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/3674485201d53f493a2977900a70367b/f8a08/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3674485201d53f493a2977900a70367b/75985/3.jpg 150w,\n/static/3674485201d53f493a2977900a70367b/f93b5/3.jpg 300w,\n/static/3674485201d53f493a2977900a70367b/f8a08/3.jpg 586w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 586px) 100vw, 586px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>&#x3C;script>タグはコピーして&#x3C;head>に貼り付けます。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.medium</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> source-han-serif-japanese<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 500<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> normal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>あとはフォントを適用したい部分で CSS をそのまま貼り付けます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/48449259d3a7f6da91d579f1e4568cc7/4e5ca/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/48449259d3a7f6da91d579f1e4568cc7/b4294/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/48449259d3a7f6da91d579f1e4568cc7/75985/4.jpg 150w,\n/static/48449259d3a7f6da91d579f1e4568cc7/f93b5/4.jpg 300w,\n/static/48449259d3a7f6da91d579f1e4568cc7/b4294/4.jpg 600w,\n/static/48449259d3a7f6da91d579f1e4568cc7/8e1fc/4.jpg 900w,\n/static/48449259d3a7f6da91d579f1e4568cc7/4e5ca/4.jpg 1079w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>もしも CSS を忘れてしまったら、\n「My Adobe Fonts」→「Web プロジェクト」→「プロジェクトを編集」を選ぶと上記の画面になるので、「CSS をコピー」でいける。</p>\n<h2 id=\"google-fonts無料\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#google-fonts%E7%84%A1%E6%96%99\" aria-label=\"google fonts無料 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Google Fonts（無料）</h2>\n<p>まずは<a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Google Fonts</a>のサイトへいきます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4283a4c63020b83aa8dfd6d51cb6df88/dd104/image-6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/4283a4c63020b83aa8dfd6d51cb6df88/0a47e/image-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4283a4c63020b83aa8dfd6d51cb6df88/8a4e8/image-6.png 150w,\n/static/4283a4c63020b83aa8dfd6d51cb6df88/5a46d/image-6.png 300w,\n/static/4283a4c63020b83aa8dfd6d51cb6df88/0a47e/image-6.png 600w,\n/static/4283a4c63020b83aa8dfd6d51cb6df88/1cfc2/image-6.png 900w,\n/static/4283a4c63020b83aa8dfd6d51cb6df88/dd104/image-6.png 1064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>検索ボックスで使用したいフォントを探します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/baef3f9ab07f71835f7117a9b05e4003/18539/image-7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/baef3f9ab07f71835f7117a9b05e4003/0a47e/image-7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/baef3f9ab07f71835f7117a9b05e4003/8a4e8/image-7.png 150w,\n/static/baef3f9ab07f71835f7117a9b05e4003/5a46d/image-7.png 300w,\n/static/baef3f9ab07f71835f7117a9b05e4003/0a47e/image-7.png 600w,\n/static/baef3f9ab07f71835f7117a9b05e4003/1cfc2/image-7.png 900w,\n/static/baef3f9ab07f71835f7117a9b05e4003/18539/image-7.png 1074w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>使いたいフォントを片っ端から「+ Select this style」します。\nもちろん複数のフォントも選べます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/348de187386005d965875c0e7316d076/d6334/5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/348de187386005d965875c0e7316d076/b4294/5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/348de187386005d965875c0e7316d076/75985/5.jpg 150w,\n/static/348de187386005d965875c0e7316d076/f93b5/5.jpg 300w,\n/static/348de187386005d965875c0e7316d076/b4294/5.jpg 600w,\n/static/348de187386005d965875c0e7316d076/8e1fc/5.jpg 900w,\n/static/348de187386005d965875c0e7316d076/d6334/5.jpg 1082w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>しかし選び過ぎには注意です。読み込みデータがその分重くなってしまいます。\n選んだ後に「必要ないな」となった時は「－」で削除します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 295px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0331dabff968be56a6a731c3f6af38e5/e4a3f/image-9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 154.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/0331dabff968be56a6a731c3f6af38e5/e4a3f/image-9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0331dabff968be56a6a731c3f6af38e5/8a4e8/image-9.png 150w,\n/static/0331dabff968be56a6a731c3f6af38e5/e4a3f/image-9.png 295w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 295px) 100vw, 295px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>使用するフォントを選んだら「Embed」を選択します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 295px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f9c692f1ec9a8c5efa50c9a028c5f88/e4a3f/image-10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 170.66666666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/8f9c692f1ec9a8c5efa50c9a028c5f88/e4a3f/image-10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f9c692f1ec9a8c5efa50c9a028c5f88/8a4e8/image-10.png 150w,\n/static/8f9c692f1ec9a8c5efa50c9a028c5f88/e4a3f/image-10.png 295w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 295px) 100vw, 295px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>&#x3C;link>タグは&#x3C;head>タグ内に貼り付けます。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.noto</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Noto Sans JP'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 400<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.ex-light</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Source Code Pro'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> monospace<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> italic<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>CSS もそのまま貼り付けますが、斜体や太さなどは追加で記述します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 288px; \n                margin-inline: 0;\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/09f98636dd18892ed3e332182c82fd5e/c14c5/7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 154.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/09f98636dd18892ed3e332182c82fd5e/c14c5/7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/09f98636dd18892ed3e332182c82fd5e/75985/7.jpg 150w,\n/static/09f98636dd18892ed3e332182c82fd5e/c14c5/7.jpg 288w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>数値等は Review の部分を見れば簡単にわかります。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-20","slug":"/32","title":"WEBフォントの使い方＜サーバー、Adobe、Google＞","tags":["css"],"thumbnail":null},"excerpt":"WEB フォントの使い方について説明します。画像が多めの説明です。 サーバーに直接フォントをアップロード フォントを準備する まず使いたいフォントをローカルで用意します。  必要ならばコンバーターを使用して変換もします。 https…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E3%82%B5%E3%83%BC%E3%83%90%E3%83%BC%E3%81%AB%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E3%83%95%E3%82%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88%E3%82%92%E3%82%A2%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89\">サーバーに直接フォントをアップロード</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E3%83%95%E3%82%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88%E3%82%92%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\">フォントを準備する</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#css-%E3%81%AE%E8%A8%98%E8%BF%B0\">CSS の記述</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#adobe-fonts%E6%9C%89%E6%96%99\">Adobe Fonts（有料）</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#google-fonts%E7%84%A1%E6%96%99\">Google Fonts（無料）</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"うさ技術"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"faa3c579-89a1-5a31-aca0-3fc4e4bf2cfa","frontmatter__slug":"/32","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"32"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1304567263","209911134","3832698534"],"slicesMap":{}}